<p>The pictures on the left are obtained from <a href="http://www12.plala.or.jp/sikoukairo/kanbe_elfeloc00.htm">this site</a> &mdash; there you'll find comments to the pictures and further information. Great thanks for taking the effort to make such accurate pictures.</p>
